<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div style="margin: 15px;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: March 30th, 2025</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we
      collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We use Google Analytics to collect information about how visitors interact
      with our website. This includes data such as:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your IP address</li>
      <li>Browser type and version</li>
      <li>Pages visited and time spent on the site</li>
      <li>Referring website addresses</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This information is collected to help us understand user behavior and
      improve our website.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      The information collected via Google Analytics is used solely for
      analytical purposes, such as:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Improving website functionality and user experience</li>
      <li>Monitoring website performance</li>
      <li>Identifying trends and usage patterns</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      Google Analytics is a third-party service that collects and processes data
      on our behalf. For more information on how Google uses your data, please
      visit the
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <p>
      You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the
      <a
        href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:webmaster@rizwaan.me">webmaster@rizwaan.me</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --heading-color: var(--text-color);
    --link-color: #4338ca;
    --link-hover-color: var(--hover-bg);
  }

  :root.dark {
    --link-color: #818cf8;
    --link-hover-color: var(--hover-bg);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  a:any-link {
    color: var(--link-color);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: var(--link-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
    background-color: transparent;
  }
</style>
